## 🗂️ Archived Files Location

The old duplicate files are archived with `.OLD` extension:
- `.agents/workflows/agent-handover.md.OLD`
- `.agents/workflows/pick-up.md.OLD`
- `.agents/skills/agent_collaboration_standard.OLD/`

To permanently delete them later:
```powershell
Remove-Item .agents/workflows/*.OLD
Remove-Item .agents/skills/*.OLD -Recurse
```

